Carlos Manuel Perez Jr, 28, was killed by a trainee corrections officer at High Desert State Prison in Indian Springs . 
  He was allegedly pitted against Andrew Jay Arevalo, 24, inside the prison . 
  Guards allegedly staged a 'gladiator-like' fight between the inmates . 
  Trainee officer fired four shots in a row at the pair . 
  Perez was killed and Arevala was left with wounds to his face . 
 